      "raw_text": "Members of some of the local\nuniens have drafted resolutions\nwhich will be forwarded to the\nAmerican Federation Of Labor for\nadoption, asking that the govern\nment establish postal savings\nbanks. The resolutions state the\npeople are at present unprotected\nfrom manipulators of stock mar\nkets and have lost confidence in\nthe Integrity of such financiers as\nHILL Morgan or Hartman."
